iske 2 logic h :- 

1. brute force :- every index value ka square kro & fir arr ko increasing order m sort kr do.

2. optimized :-  two pointer approach se. left 0 se start kro aur right len-1 se.
                  compare karo arr left & right index ki values ko. ek new array banao. new-array ka index = len-1
		  yadi left index ki value bdi h to usse new-array m store kro aur left++ & new-array ka idx--;
                  yadi right index ki value bdi h to usse new-array m store kro aur right-- & new-array ka idx--
